 and is being merged with another profile. Please sign-in to a different profile.",y2="Retry merge",v2="Terminate merge";var jse="Merge complete";var Qse="You can refresh the page to check the merge status.",Yse="Profile merge record not found",Wse='Unable to find your profile merge. Please refresh the page. If the problem is still there, please contact <a href="https://learn.microsoft.com/training/support/troubleshooting#report-feedback">customer support</a>.',Kse="A previous merge attempt is preventing this action",Jse="One of the profiles you are trying to merge is currently being merged with another profile. Please log into both profiles to check the status.";var Zse="Your profiles have been successfully merged.",Xse="We ran into a problem merging your source profile (username: {sourceUser}) to your destination profile (username: {destinationUser}).",eie="Some of your data might have been merged in the process, so it is expected if you find some data disappearing from your source profile and appearing on your destination profile.",tie="You can choose one of the following actions:",nie="<b>{terminateMergeText}</b>: It will stop and quit the merge process. You will be able to use both profiles as usual and can trigger a new merge at any time. The data that already merged will remain on your destination profile.",oie="<b>{retryMergeText}</b>: It will re-run the merging process for you once more. Your source profile will be locked during the merging process.",rie="Merging in progress. It may take several minutes to complete.",sie="Your merge has been terminated.";var iie="Microsoft MVP";var aie="Microsoft Learn Student Ambassador";var lie="Sign in with a different account";var cie="Welcome to Q&A!",uie="Get personalized updates on topics you care about",die="Build your reputation while helping others",pie="Connect instantly with people who share your interests";var mie="Without completing registration, you will not be able to post or ask a question on Q&A.";var gie=